{"tid":164541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"非吹水，樓上有斬野聲","createTime":"2017-03-20T17:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T17:32:18.000Z","uid":14423,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b87f50f0206008c6d74f6194306b90d3a82d6c8f","tid":164541,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"上上吓連登，突然聽到有斬野聲<br />\n平時間唔中都有聽到，但突然諗一諗<br />\n依家成一點喎<br />\n然後就無左斬野聲<br />\n但到依家為止，都仲有少少搬野聲<br />\n唔敢再諗，都係訓覺<br />\n但我打到哩度，又再有斬野聲，但個聲無之前咁大<br />\n其實會唔會係果啲乜鬼水管影響？"},{"pid":"400367651a3ed8918431695da7cf862975c2bb79","tid":164541,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"一定唔係樓上碎緊屍，樓主可以安心訓教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c5bfc1a5a676f0170a575b616947091257849f","tid":164541,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"應該唔會嘅"},{"pid":"9f704e7f374a141bb82952c444f99308b1338474","tid":164541,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"報警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f001e789f09fcd165867afc2b461279db27ebc8","tid":164541,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3bbf3a1520d92054eac7a41fd905bef6571b58","tid":164541,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"我頭上個天花板無啦啦有一吓搬櫈聲"},{"pid":"92534b2016f727354b828fa8fab3959ac9bf6b0a","tid":164541,"uid":12603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我頭上個天花板無啦啦有一吓搬櫈聲</blockquote><br />\n我有時夜晚都會聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8ad55ed4549d0ebbbf4b60c3a9d7fef0eeff48","tid":164541,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re